at burst emission will need to account\nfor the increasing diversity in the burst polarization properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Sep 2021 17:56:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 15:26:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-01"}
