 the electron beams used for electron impact studies, as\nwell as reporting the preliminary results obtained during electron irradiation\nand thermal processing of selected ices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Sep 2021 22:34:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-27"}
