f global constraints as\nwell as how we solve the resulting constraint system. We report on the\nevaluation of these concepts and the Iris tool with domain experts from\ndifferent companies in the automotive value chain based on the industrial case\nof a smart sensing electrical fuse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2021 08:59:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-27"}
