order phase transition which induces the spontaneous\ndecompactification of the shrinking dimension before the instability manifests,\nfavouring instead a branch of singular solutions. The light dilaton resonance\nappears only along a metastable portion of the branch of confining backgrounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2021 13:18:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-27"}
