lize this mathematical\ntheory to treat the quantum field theory of Einsteins's gravity (EG). Because\nwe are using a Gupta-Feynman inspired EG Lagrangian, we are able to evade the\nintricacies of Yang-Mills theories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2021 00:30:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-05"}
